character.name:
**Create an isometric pixel art character (64×32 style) designed for a fantasy game.
The character is a young elf archer.
Not realistic, not too cartoon → balanced fantasy style.
He must fit perfectly in a bright colorful world with grass, trees, and dirt paths.

Requirements :
– isometric perspective
– simple and clean pixel art
– visible silhouette
– medium-size character (not chibi)
– lightly pointed elf ears
– light leather armor
– green or brown clothing
– a wooden bow in hand
– a quiver on his back
– neutral idle pose facing the bottom-right direction
– clean outline, no background, no shadow
– pixel perfect and compatible with 64×32 isometric tiles**
